## Cards

Cards are implemented using styled `Border` controls with drop shadows.

### Standard Card

```xaml
<Border Style="{StaticResource Card}">
    <StackPanel>
        <TextBlock Text="Card Title" Style="{StaticResource TitleTextStyle}"/>
        <TextBlock Text="Card content goes here"/>
    </StackPanel>
</Border>

<!-- Alternative: StandardCard is an alias for Card -->
<Border Style="{StaticResource StandardCard}">
    <!-- Content -->
</Border>
```

Features:
- White background
- 8px corner radius
- 24px padding
- Drop shadow (Dp2 equivalent)

### Metric Card

For dashboard metrics and statistics:

```xaml
<Border Style="{StaticResource MetricCard}"
        BorderBrush="{StaticResource SuccessBrush}"
        BorderThickness="4,0,0,0">
    <Grid>
        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        </Grid.RowDefinitions>
        
        <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" 
                   Text="URLs Crawled" 
                   Style="{StaticResource BodyTextStyle}"/>
        <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" 
                   Text="1,234" 
                   Style="{StaticResource DisplayTextStyle}"
                   FontSize="32"/>
    </Grid>
</Border>
```

Features:
- 16px padding (more compact than standard card)
- Lighter drop shadow (Dp1 equivalent)
- Often combined with colored left border for accent

### Info Card

For informational messages and hints:

```xaml
<Border Style="{StaticResource InfoCard}">
    <TextBlock Text="Helpful information appears here"/>
</Border>
```

Features:
- Light blue background (`#E3F2FD`)
- No shadow
- 6px corner radius

### Shadow Elevation

Cards use `DropShadowEffect` to simulate Material Design elevation:

| Elevation | Blur Radius | Shadow Depth | Opacity | Usage |
|-----------|-------------|--------------|---------|-------|
| Dp0 | - | - | - | No shadow (Info cards) |
| Dp1 | 4 | 1 | 0.08 | Metric cards |
| Dp2 | 8 | 2 | 0.10 | Standard cards |
| Dp4 | 12 | 3 | 0.12 | Elevated cards |
| Dp8 | 24 | 4 | 0.15 | Modal overlays |

